= Check Real Size =
Yo must change directory into the correct folder first. For your home folder. Depending on which one you want to check.

{{CodeSelect|code=
cd ~
}}

Or.

{{CodeSelect|code=
cd /var/lib/libvirt/images/
}}

Run.

{{CodeSelect|code=
du -h Whonix-Gateway-*.qcow2 
}}

Should show something like this.

<pre>
2.5G    Whonix-Gateway-*.qcow2
</pre>

= Check Apparent Size =
Run.

{{CodeSelect|code=
du -h --apparent-size Whonix-Gateway-*.qcow2 
}}

Should show something like this.

<pre>
101G    Whonix-Gateway-*.qcow2
</pre>

